<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM6.1">
<l>ērmalarp pūṅkuḻa lāyarmāta reṉaippala ruḷḷaviv vūriluṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>mārvu taḻuvutaṟ kācaiyiṉmai yaṟintaṟin tēyuṉṟaṉ poyyaikkēṭṭuk</l>
<l>kūrmaḻaipōṟpaṉik kūtaleytik kūci naṭuṅki yamuṉaiyāṟṟil</l>
<l>vārmaṇaṟ kuṉṟiṟ pularaniṉṟēṉ vācutē vāvuṉ varavupārttē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Knowing of [my own] absence of desire for embracing Your chest,</l>
<l rend="indent">in this town where there are so many cowherd women</l>
<l rend="indent">with curling hair [adorned with] beautiful, blooming flowers,</l>
<l>despite knowing [it], listening to Your lie,</l>
<l>I stood, as it dawned on the long sand bank on the river Yamunā,</l>
<l>feeling the coolness of the abundant rain-like dew, getting shy, shivering,</l>
<l>O Vāsudeva! expecting Your arrival.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
